"You can try Quarkus Data Hibernate today from Quarkus 3.37.0.\n"
"It will also ship as part of https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/52020[Quarkus 4.0]."
msgstr "Ya puede probar Quarkus Data Hibernate a partir de la versión 3.37.0 de Quarkus. Además, se incluirá como parte de link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/52020[Quarkus 4.0] ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-15-introducing-quarkus-data.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Give it a try and let us know what you think. Feedback is welcome on https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Quarkus.20Data/with/602434654[Zulip] or via https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[GitHub issues]."
msgstr "Pruébelo y díganos qué le parece. Agradecemos sus comentarios en link:https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Quarkus.20Data/with/602434654[Zulip] o a través de link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[las incidencias de GitHub] ."

